# Build and RUN the suite on C++ with full dead-code elimination (-dce full).
# This PROVES the reflection / Int64 type-dispatch in the encoder and the AsMap
# string-key detection survive DCE at runtime (not merely at type-check), which
# is the crux of the production-readiness work.
#
#   haxe tests_dce.hxml
#
-dce full
-lib utest
-lib hxcpp
-cp .
-cp tests
-main org.msgpack.tests.MsgPackTests
-cpp tests/cpp_dce
-cmd echo "Running C++ (-dce full) tests..." && tests/cpp_dce/MsgPackTests
